			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p><strong>Think Ahead</strong></p>

<p><a href="http://thinkahead.org/" target="_blank">Think Ahead</a> is a new fast-track programme, for graduates and career-changers remarkable enough to make a real difference to people with mental health problems.</p>

<p>We're searching for exceptional people to become mental health social workers. You will study for a Post-Graduate Diploma and Master's qualification in Social Work from the University of York. You'll be paid to work in an expert team alongside clinical professionals, study for a master's degree and develop your leadership skills.</p>

<p>We're here to find remarkable people, who'll do remarkable things. Think Ahead: apply your mind to mental health.</p>

<p>Applications are now open to take part in our two-year programme from July 2016.<p>

<p>.</p>
			
			
			<td align="right" valign="top"><img src="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/Think_Ahead_logo.JPG" alt="" width="200" height="225" border="0"></td>

<tr>


</tr>
			
			<tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p><strong>Engagement Coordinator - The Challenge (NCS programme)</strong><br>
			The Challenge currently has a number of exciting opportunities for enthusiastic and driven 'Engagement Coordinators' to join our fast paced Sales Teams across the country. Using strong communication and presentation skills, you will be engaging and recruiting 15-17 year olds to join our National Citizen Service programme (NCS) which will help build their skills for work, life and transition into adulthood.</p>

<p>The role is a permanent, paid position which gives you all the tools you need to build a career in the UK not for profit sector. We have vacancies in our London, West Midlands, Epsom, Reading, Birmingham and Leeds offices. If you are interested in this fantastic position, we would love to hear from you. Please send us your CV and a covering letter outlining your suitability for the role to: <strong><i>recruitment@the-challenge.org</i></strong></p><br>
						
